descriptionHtml:
*Basic Run-Down*
-I made this mod because I couldn\'t find a single Farkas savegame, so for all of those who are looking for one, here you are. I took many high quality pictures and made him from that. Enjoy. :)
*Installation*
Just extract the savegame file into the directory: MyGames/Skyrim/Save Games.
*Un-Installation*
Just simply delete the file from your Save Games folder.
*Recommended Mods*
-No More Blocky Faces
-Detailed Faces
-Detailed Bodies
-Detailed Lips
-DALLS_Better_Nords
:) Have fun. If you wish to edit him, just open the console with the \"~\" key and type in \"showracemenu\".
author: Shibbytester84
